  * [[https://sourceforge.net/projects/mysql-admin/|MySQL-Admin]] & [[http://www.alwins-world.de/wiki/programs/kmysqladmin|kmysqladmin]] -> 2 outils pour MySQL non maintenus
  * [[http://sqlitebrowser.sourceforge.net/|SQLite Database Browser]]
